name: D.E.M.O.N.S: Getting Summoned Weekly isn't so Bad
summary: “Kat, you have a tail” said Lily“Look, Lily, it really isn’t that big of a concern” said Kat“You.Have.A.TAIL KAT” said Lily “How is this not a concern to you?”“Well, the dream I had was a bit weird as well, but if I’m honest, I’m mainly worried about the floating text that’s on fire” said Kat“THE What?” said Lily---------------------------------------------------Join Kat on her dimension hopping adventures as she fullfills her demonic duty and answers the call of the summoner. Each week Kat will get involved with new strange situations and oppurtunites that await her. During the week she'll have her best friend Lily, and perhaps a little help from Sylvie to figure out what's she supposed to do with her life now that she's becoming a demon.
author: Vongrak
